<p>The design system must be universally accessible. This means components and patterns to work on every browser and device that users access our services on.</p>

## Test for compatibility
<p>Components and patterns don’t have to look perfect in every browser but users must be able to access and use all the information and features they need, regardless of which browser they use.</p>
